WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:08.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I can't believe flowers 
can bloom even in this dump.</font>

2
00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:10.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Delmon.</font>

3
00:00:10.730 --> 00:00:14.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thanks to your tireless hard work.</font>

4
00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:17.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I finally get to see the real thing.</font>

5
00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:19.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thank you.</font>

6
00:00:19.470 --> 00:00:22.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Nah. One's not enough.</font>

7
00:00:27.520 --> 00:00:31.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's cover our whole house in those flowers.</font>

8
00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:45.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Big Man!</font>

9
00:00:46.030 --> 00:00:48.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">My... sweet Rudo?</font>

10
00:00:49.030 --> 00:00:51.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And...</font>

11
00:00:51.210 --> 00:00:52.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Girl!</font>

12
00:00:56.590 --> 00:00:58.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">As you can see.</font>

13
00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:01.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo's got lots of fans now.</font>

14
00:01:01.990 --> 00:01:04.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you still gonna try 
to bring the party down?</font>

15
00:01:08.860 --> 00:01:10.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll ask you all...</font>

16
00:01:10.580 --> 00:01:12.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">to endure this.</font>

17
00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:16.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Vital instrument—Tokushin.</font>

18
00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:30.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why. you...</font>

19
00:01:31.550 --> 00:01:34.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sons of bitches!</font>

20
00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:39.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll never let you hurt her again!</font>

21
00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:43.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Net.</font>

22
00:02:02.270 --> 00:02:04.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wh-What is this stuff?</font>

23
00:02:04.440 --> 00:02:05.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Rope?</font>

24
00:02:06.850 --> 00:02:10.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Aw. look what you did to Amo's room!</font>

25
00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:15.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do something. you guys!</font>

26
00:02:19.370 --> 00:02:21.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It would better not to move so much.</font>

27
00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:27.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The more you move. the tighter it'll hold you.</font>

28
00:02:28.860 --> 00:02:31.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm very sorry...</font>

29
00:02:36.550 --> 00:02:39.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I was hoping the pain
 would snap you out of it.</font>

30
00:02:39.530 --> 00:02:41.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but I guess not.</font>

31
00:02:41.910 --> 00:02:45.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What a meanie!</font>

32
00:02:45.050 --> 00:02:50.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You wanna experiment so bad. 
you'll hurt your own friends to do it?</font>

33
00:02:51.580 --> 00:02:54.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But the experiment failed.</font>

34
00:02:54.780 --> 00:02:57.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">To help Amo. they'll find a way to escape.</font>

35
00:02:57.630 --> 00:02:59.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">no matter how much pain 
it puts them through.</font>

36
00:02:59.710 --> 00:03:02.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's gonna get bloody!</font>

37
00:03:02.270 --> 00:03:05.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">My vital instrument is a distaff.</font>

38
00:03:06.990 --> 00:03:08.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do you know?</font>

39
00:03:10.630 --> 00:03:14.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Its a staff used for winding thread.</font>

40
00:03:31.390 --> 00:03:33.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Winding complete!</font>

41
00:03:37.600 --> 00:03:38.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And...</font>

42
00:03:42.730 --> 00:03:45.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Psycho lady capture complete.</font>

43
00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:31.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Go on.</font>

44
00:05:32.220 --> 00:05:34.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Return them to normal already.</font>

45
00:05:35.150 --> 00:05:36.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Better make it snappy.</font>

46
00:05:37.380 --> 00:05:40.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm not likin' how damn surreal this looks.</font>

47
00:05:40.330 --> 00:05:43.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Also. I didn't do much this time.</font>

48
00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:45.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's untrue.</font>

49
00:05:45.630 --> 00:05:50.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Knowledge that she was 
fighting multiple enemies</font>

50
00:05:50.700 --> 00:05:53.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">would have put a mental burden 
on our opponent.</font>

51
00:05:54.020 --> 00:05:57.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And I think calling her "cow" 
was quite effective.</font>

52
00:05:57.870 --> 00:05:59.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tomme!</font>

53
00:06:02.550 --> 00:06:05.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You were wearing your mask? Thank goodness.</font>

54
00:06:06.380 --> 00:06:07.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How's Enjin?</font>

55
00:06:08.990 --> 00:06:10.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Still nothing.</font>

56
00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:14.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I put the mask on him. but...</font>

57
00:06:14.190 --> 00:06:18.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see. We'd better get 
the med team to look at him.</font>

58
00:06:26.310 --> 00:06:30.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hurts... It hurts...</font>

59
00:06:31.850 --> 00:06:34.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No one's been this rough with Amo in ages!</font>

60
00:06:34.810 --> 00:06:37.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're awful... awful...</font>

61
00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:41.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Meanie. meanie. meanie. meanie!</font>

62
00:06:47.790 --> 00:06:51.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Help Amo!</font>

63
00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:54.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's starting up again.</font>

64
00:06:54.700 --> 00:06:55.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But nobody can move—</font>

65
00:06:55.930 --> 00:06:58.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Unforgivable.</font>

66
00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:01.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Unforgivable!</font>

67
00:07:01.650 --> 00:07:04.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You better get ready.</font>

68
00:07:04.490 --> 00:07:07.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm gonna get outta here...</font>

69
00:07:08.110 --> 00:07:16.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and kill the shit out of every last one of you!</font>

70
00:07:29.200 --> 00:07:30.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Enough.</font>

71
00:07:31.740 --> 00:07:34.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You like her that much. do you?</font>

72
00:07:35.970 --> 00:07:38.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Then I'll release you.</font>

73
00:07:48.370 --> 00:07:51.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What the hell?!</font>

74
00:08:34.340 --> 00:08:35.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tamsy.</font>

75
00:08:36.790 --> 00:08:40.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You went way too damn far.</font>

76
00:08:58.270 --> 00:09:00.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'd say that's handled.</font>

77
00:09:01.400 --> 00:09:04.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Handled?! You killed your own—</font>

78
00:09:06.460 --> 00:09:08.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">See? See?</font>

79
00:09:09.330 --> 00:09:13.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is what happens when 
people don't just talk to Amo!</font>

80
00:09:15.130 --> 00:09:20.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Your true nature shows itself 
even when you try to hide it!</font>

81
00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:25.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They're all on death's door 
because you're so awful!</font>

82
00:09:25.620 --> 00:09:29.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Zero harmony with your friends at all!</font>

83
00:09:40.570 --> 00:09:41.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh?</font>

84
00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:44.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Zanka. did you forget the thing?</font>

85
00:09:46.520 --> 00:09:49.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wait. I think you did.</font>

86
00:09:49.990 --> 00:09:54.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They're all allowed to reduce damage 
from one hit. even a fatal one.</font>

87
00:09:57.060 --> 00:09:59.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I mean. remember?</font>

88
00:09:59.870 --> 00:10:03.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We all got the spell drawn on us. right?</font>

89
00:10:03.770 --> 00:10:05.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">By Remlin.</font>

90
00:10:06.340 --> 00:10:09.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's right. We're all fine.</font>

91
00:10:09.250 --> 00:10:10.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Including me.</font>

92
00:10:13.130 --> 00:10:16.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll be taking these boots. if you please.</font>

93
00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:38.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I hope they got the info about the border.</font>

94
00:10:38.520 --> 00:10:40.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">B-Boss...</font>

95
00:10:40.830 --> 00:10:45.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Given the people we sent. 
I doubt there will be a problem.</font>

96
00:10:45.990 --> 00:10:49.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You look rather unhappy. still.</font>

97
00:10:50.410 --> 00:10:55.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is it because of what you saw in Rudo?</font>

98
00:10:58.630 --> 00:11:00.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why don't you tell me?</font>

99
00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:08.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What did you see when 
you first laid eyes on Rudo?</font>

100
00:11:12.920 --> 00:11:19.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It really ticks me off 
when people only wear one sock.</font>

101
00:11:19.050 --> 00:11:19.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh?</font>

102
00:11:19.980 --> 00:11:21.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey...</font>

103
00:11:21.370 --> 00:11:23.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you not wearing socks at all?</font>

104
00:11:24.550 --> 00:11:25.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Give that back!</font>

105
00:11:25.920 --> 00:11:27.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That belongs to Amo!</font>

106
00:11:27.420 --> 00:11:31.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Give it back! Give it back!</font>

107
00:11:29.060 --> 00:11:30.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Fine. fine!</font>

108
00:11:31.550 --> 00:11:32.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You...</font>

109
00:11:32.830 --> 00:11:34.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't you touch that boot!</font>

110
00:11:34.420 --> 00:11:36.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It'll lose that person's smell...</font>

111
00:11:36.780 --> 00:11:37.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">"That person"?</font>

112
00:11:37.770 --> 00:11:39.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Give it back!</font>

113
00:11:44.460 --> 00:11:46.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Holy shit!</font>

114
00:11:46.410 --> 00:11:48.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't sniff it. you jerk!</font>

115
00:11:48.380 --> 00:11:50.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How long has Enjin been healed?</font>

116
00:11:50.310 --> 00:11:51.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}You were wearing this stinky thing?</font>

117
00:11:50.980 --> 00:11:54.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Healing internal hemorrhage 
with a spell is something else.</font>

118
00:11:51.830 --> 00:11:52.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Am I gonna survive this stench?</font>

119
00:11:52.930 --> 00:11:58.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Give it back! Give it back!</font>

120
00:11:54.780 --> 00:11:58.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He was fine when 
I started administering aid.</font>

121
00:11:58.090 --> 00:12:01.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Stop it! Just stop!</font>

122
00:11:58.090 --> 00:12:02.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He was playing possum 
until he could see his chance.</font>

123
00:12:01.290 --> 00:12:02.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Oh. shut up already!</font>

124
00:12:02.660 --> 00:12:04.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Give it back!</font>

125
00:12:02.970 --> 00:12:04.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

126
00:12:04.830 --> 00:12:08.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Cancel your ability and return 
everyone to normal. and I will.{front}</font>

127
00:12:13.460 --> 00:12:17.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo can't use her power with just one.</font>

128
00:12:18.380 --> 00:12:22.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So everyone won't protect Amo now.</font>

129
00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:35.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What in the world have I been doing?</font>

130
00:12:37.770 --> 00:12:40.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Looks like the spell did its trick.</font>

131
00:12:40.790 --> 00:12:43.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Remlin did good work.</font>

132
00:12:43.910 --> 00:12:46.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tamsy. Zanka.</font>

133
00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:51.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What happened back there?</font>

134
00:12:51.690 --> 00:12:54.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Glad to see you're back in your right mind.</font>

135
00:12:54.930 --> 00:12:59.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You were just affected 
by that woman—Amo's—power.</font>

136
00:12:59.500 --> 00:13:03.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A smell that makes you remember 
happy times with someone you love.</font>

137
00:13:04.660 --> 00:13:10.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She used it to make you think 
she was that person.</font>

138
00:13:10.160 --> 00:13:12.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It was quite difficult.</font>

139
00:13:14.890 --> 00:13:16.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

140
00:13:17.350 --> 00:13:23.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Then... she hasn't come back to life after all.</font>

141
00:13:25.050 --> 00:13:26.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

142
00:13:28.980 --> 00:13:32.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There's somethin' nasty about her power.</i></font>

143
00:13:33.930 --> 00:13:38.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>All the more for those who've lost 
someone important to them.</i></font>

144
00:13:39.510 --> 00:13:43.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The richer your memories 
of those happy times are...</i></font>

145
00:13:44.970 --> 00:13:48.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The harsher the reality you return to.</i></font>

146
00:13:51.060 --> 00:13:53.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Nasty as hell.</i></font>

147
00:13:57.760 --> 00:14:00.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Everyone's got masks on. right?</font>

148
00:14:00.590 --> 00:14:01.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Here.</font>

149
00:14:05.230 --> 00:14:07.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey. What now. Enjin?</font>

150
00:14:08.300 --> 00:14:12.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Even if we give up on getting info and leave. 
she's way too dangerous.</font>

151
00:14:12.830 --> 00:14:14.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We can't leave her out here.</font>

152
00:14:16.310 --> 00:14:21.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But outside of her instrument. 
she's just an ordinary. powerless girl.</font>

153
00:14:22.370 --> 00:14:26.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And I'd feel weird about taking 
the instrument that means so much to her.</font>

154
00:14:27.060 --> 00:14:29.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's just try to convince her 
not to hurt anyone—</font>

155
00:14:29.580 --> 00:14:31.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh. brother.</font>

156
00:14:33.260 --> 00:14:35.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo feels sick.</font>

157
00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:38.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo's whole house got ruined.</font>

158
00:14:38.250 --> 00:14:39.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh. brother!</font>

159
00:14:39.980 --> 00:14:43.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Doesn't anybody here feel guilty?!</font>

160
00:14:44.610 --> 00:14:47.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The hell is wrong with you?!</font>

161
00:14:56.290 --> 00:14:57.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Rudo?</font>

162
00:14:59.350 --> 00:15:03.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've seen a lot of people in my time.</font>

163
00:15:03.590 --> 00:15:08.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But what I saw in Rudo. I've never seen before.</font>

164
00:15:09.140 --> 00:15:11.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's not just his gloves.</font>

165
00:15:13.050 --> 00:15:14.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What's unusual about him is...</font>

166
00:15:17.500 --> 00:15:19.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You took your mask off?</font>

167
00:15:19.800 --> 00:15:24.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You can't get enough of Amo's smell. huh?</font>

168
00:15:42.510 --> 00:15:44.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What in the world...</font>

169
00:15:53.050 --> 00:15:56.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's something growing inside of Rudo.</font>

170
00:15:57.620 --> 00:16:01.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Put simply. it's like... yes...</font>

171
00:16:02.970 --> 00:16:05.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's like something 
that could destroy the world...</font>

172
00:16:06.150 --> 00:16:10.120
<font face="Arial Black" size="20"><b><font size="8">Episode 12
</font></b></font>

173
00:16:06.150 --> 00:16:10.120
<font face="Arial Black" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="35">Something Like a Curse</font></b></font>

174
00:16:06.410 --> 00:16:08.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Something like a curse.</font>

175
00:16:14.100 --> 00:16:15.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey!</font>

176
00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:17.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Rudo. enough! Calm down!</font>

177
00:16:21.870 --> 00:16:23.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's enough!</font>

178
00:16:23.980 --> 00:16:27.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We know how to cancel out her ability.</font>

179
00:16:27.040 --> 00:16:29.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's no need to go that far.</font>

180
00:16:31.100 --> 00:16:33.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Besides. she's a girl.</font>

181
00:16:33.940 --> 00:16:35.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Who gives a shit?</font>

182
00:16:38.830 --> 00:16:42.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Because she's a woman. 
I'm not allowed to fight back?</font>

183
00:16:42.930 --> 00:16:47.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Because she's a woman. I'm supposed to shut up 
and let her kill people I care about?</font>

184
00:16:55.180 --> 00:16:56.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I can't do that.</font>

185
00:16:56.910 --> 00:16:58.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's not what I mean!</font>

186
00:16:58.870 --> 00:17:01.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're beating up on someone who's powerless—</font>

187
00:17:01.370 --> 00:17:02.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Powerless. my ass!</font>

188
00:17:03.770 --> 00:17:05.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's a Giver!</font>

189
00:17:06.020 --> 00:17:09.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She tricked us and almost got us all killed.</font>

190
00:17:10.540 --> 00:17:12.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">However she looks on the outside.</font>

191
00:17:12.930 --> 00:17:17.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">inside she was laughing at us. 
stomping down on us.</font>

192
00:17:18.100 --> 00:17:20.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She deserves a damn pummeling.</font>

193
00:17:29.910 --> 00:17:32.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

194
00:17:33.150 --> 00:17:35.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So that's your thought process.</font>

195
00:17:36.540 --> 00:17:37.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So...</font>

196
00:17:37.740 --> 00:17:41.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How do we get the info now?</font>

197
00:18:06.610 --> 00:18:09.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's have a little talk. shall we?</font>

198
00:18:11.510 --> 00:18:15.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tomme. Get her patched up. would you?</font>

199
00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:16.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. sir!</font>

200
00:18:38.920 --> 00:18:40.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why aren't you saying anything?</font>

201
00:18:40.980 --> 00:18:41.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh?</font>

202
00:18:44.420 --> 00:18:49.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well... it looks like you've realized 
what's going on already.</font>

203
00:18:50.560 --> 00:18:55.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You got emotional and forgot 
why we came here. right?</font>

204
00:18:59.390 --> 00:19:00.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I...</font>

205
00:19:02.200 --> 00:19:05.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The whole time I was in the Sphere...</font>

206
00:19:06.800 --> 00:19:09.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I always had to take it.</font>

207
00:19:09.000 --> 00:19:13.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No matter what people said to me. 
I was told to hold my temper. To endure it.</font>

208
00:19:14.510 --> 00:19:17.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But when they sent me 
to the Ground. I realized...</font>

209
00:19:18.250 --> 00:19:20.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If I tried to hold it in. I'd lose.</font>

210
00:19:21.720 --> 00:19:24.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And just now. I realized...</font>

211
00:19:25.810 --> 00:19:29.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've gone back to how I was.</font>

212
00:19:30.570 --> 00:19:32.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The version of me before I learned patience.</font>

213
00:19:32.990 --> 00:19:38.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">who just hit the people around me 
with all the darkness welling up inside me...</font>

214
00:19:39.370 --> 00:19:43.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">After all this crap I've been though. 
I haven't really changed.</font>

215
00:19:44.200 --> 00:19:49.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Above or below. any growth I think 
I've gone through is just an illusion.</font>

216
00:19:49.710 --> 00:19:51.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm still a shitty little brat!</font>

217
00:19:55.240 --> 00:19:56.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">As for me...</font>

218
00:19:57.340 --> 00:20:00.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I like hot ladies.</font>

219
00:20:03.350 --> 00:20:10.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Smarter than me. with curves and 
sex appeal and a forgiving personality.</font>

220
00:20:10.030 --> 00:20:11.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I love 'em so damn much.</font>

221
00:20:12.250 --> 00:20:16.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But ladies and kids with complicated needs. 
I have a lot more trouble with.</font>

222
00:20:17.500 --> 00:20:21.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Y'know? That's not a thing 
women are happy to hear. right?</font>

223
00:20:22.390 --> 00:20:26.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The fact that I can't hide that stuff 
is one of my bad traits.</font>

224
00:20:27.020 --> 00:20:31.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Even we adults have tons of crap 
we need to grow out of.</font>

225
00:20:32.060 --> 00:20:38.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So if you want to grow. that "realization" 
is the thing you really need.</font>

226
00:20:39.580 --> 00:20:43.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I was brought face-to-face 
with my faults ages ago.</font>

227
00:20:43.770 --> 00:20:46.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You realized yours on your own.</font>

228
00:20:47.040 --> 00:20:48.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Which means...</font>

229
00:20:49.740 --> 00:20:53.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Heck. man. we've got nowhere to go but up!</font>

230
00:20:57.740 --> 00:21:00.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's go apologize together later.</font>

231
00:21:03.980 --> 00:21:05.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sorry about that.</font>

232
00:21:06.380 --> 00:21:09.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We didn't mean to take things this far.</font>

233
00:21:10.340 --> 00:21:12.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I really am sorry.</font>

234
00:21:19.780 --> 00:21:23.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm happy to talk as much as you like. 
if you don't mind me!</font>

235
00:21:24.730 --> 00:21:27.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I love talking romance too!</font>

236
00:21:31.950 --> 00:21:34.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You'd make a good mama.</font>

237
00:21:35.340 --> 00:21:36.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You think?</font>

238
00:21:37.290 --> 00:21:40.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo's mama was a good mama too.</font>

239
00:21:40.030 --> 00:21:44.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Mama is the reason Amo met her first love.</font>

240
00:21:45.990 --> 00:21:48.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And that Amo got her treasure.</font>

241
00:21:49.650 --> 00:21:53.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And saw the angel that goes between 
the Sphere and the Ground.</font>

242
00:21:53.290 --> 00:21:55.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see. The angel...</font>

243
00:21:57.610 --> 00:21:59.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The Sphere and the Ground?</font>

244
00:22:00.800 --> 00:22:02.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey...</font>

245
00:22:02.940 --> 00:22:05.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What'd you just say?</font>
